These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
City: berlin, rome
Birthday: june, july
1. City:rome is on the left or right of City:berlin##3
2. Birthday:july is on the right of City:rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| City   | rome  | berlin |
| Birthday       | june | july |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
Transport: motorbike, bike
Game: snooker, whist
1. Game:whist is on the left or right of Transport:bike##3
2. Transport:bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Transport   | motorbike | bike |
| Game      | whist     | snooker  |

 #################################
 
